# M6 P02 — jetpack FX sync test (host).
#
# Reactor map; host Burst, client Standard. Both spawn adjacent on
# open floor (well clear of the central pillar). Host triggers boost
# to capture the orange spike; client just sustains. Both windows
# screenshot matching ticks for side-by-side visual diff.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/2p_jet_fx.host
network host 24201
name HostBurst
map reactor
loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Burst

# Reactor floor at y=1216; spawn pelvis 40 px above (y=1176). Central
# pillar at x=1632..1888 — keep well west.
spawn_at 400 1176
peer_spawn 1 650 1176

# Aim at the client's chest height to the right (cursor parked, no
# aim transitions during the test).
aim 1100 1140

# Phase 1: settle on floor (game ticks 0..40).
# Phase 2 (game ticks 50+): both press jet. shotmode tick 240 maps
# to game tick ~50 here per 2p_combat's timing convention. Going
# generous: press at shotmode 240 (well past lobby + countdown).
at 240 press jet
at 245 shot t245_ignition

# Sustain hold; capture mid-jet.
at 270 shot t270_sustain

# Boost: press DASH on the Burst host. Boost lasts 24 ticks
# (0.4s × 60 Hz).
at 280 press dash
at 285 shot t285_boost_early
at 290 release dash
at 295 shot t295_boost_mid
at 310 shot t310_post_boost

# Release jet and fall.
at 340 release jet
at 360 shot t360_falling
at 400 shot t400_grounded_again

at 460 end

contact_sheet sheet cols 3 cell 640 360
